@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_omuels(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.88
    v1 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.16 * tmp + 0.38)) * ((tmp + 0.31 + tmp + 0.41) * (v0 + 0.06 - v1 + 0.93)))
    tmp = (tmp / v1)
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.11 + v2 + 0.29)))
    tmp = wp.exp(v1)
    data[tid] = v0
